{#- ═══ F2 PRICING DETAIL — monthly bookkeeping (canonical Sheet-0 figures).
    t-bofu→t-prose. Every baseline heading verbatim; canonical tier ranges EXACT
    (tldr + `tiers` data, untouched). #pbk-tldr-body speakable preserved.
